dismissalComment.html: this one's good! Straighter ball dug in towards the pads and Maiden misses the defensive shot, the appeal goes up and the umpire raises the finger quickly

dismissalText.commentary: Preston Mommsen lbw b BAW Mendis 8 (24b 1x4 0x6 45m) SR: 33.33

dismissalComment.html: goes to sweep through the leg-side and can't make contact, the ball hits the pads and straightens up in front of middle-stump

dismissalText.commentary: Gordon Drummond b Malinga 5 (21b 0x4 0x6 36m) SR: 23.8

dismissalComment.html: Malinga persisting with the yorkers finally gets one through Drummond and removes the off-stump

dismissalText.commentary: Majid Haq c †Chandimal b Prasad 34 (61b 5x4 0x6 68m) SR: 55.73

dismissalComment.html: goes to drive the wider ball, thin edge which the keeper gathers down low to his left, great resistance from Haq, he exits for 34

dismissalText.commentary: Gordon Goudie c BMAJ Mendis b Malinga 0 (3b 0x4 0x6 4m) SR: 0
